<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Oops! Page Not Found</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/img/icon.png" type="image/png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/normalize/5.0.0/normalize.min.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap');

        :root {
            --primary-color: #00FFFB;
            --secondary-color: #121212;
            --gradient-start: #00fffb68;
            --gradient-end: #ffffff;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body, html {
            height: 100%;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .error-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gradient-start), var(--gradient-end));
            perspective: 1000px;
        }

        .error-content {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 40px;
            background: #ffffffc9;
            border-radius: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.17) 0px -23px 25px 0px inset, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 0px -36px 30px 0px inset, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px -79px 40px 0px inset, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06) 0px 2px 1px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.09) 0px 4px 2px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.09) 0px 8px 4px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.09) 0px 16px 8px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.09) 0px 32px 16px;
            /* transform: rotateX(10deg); */
            transition: all 0.5s ease;
        }

        .error-content:hover {
            transform: rotateX(0deg) scale(1.05);
           /* box-shadow: rgba(50, 50, 93, 0.25) 0px 30px 60px -12px inset, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) 0px 18px 36px -18px inset; */
        }

        .error-number {
            font-size: 200px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
            text-shadow: 5px 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--primary-color));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .error-message {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .error-description {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.7);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .home-button {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            color: var(--primary-color);
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .home-button:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .floating-elements {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .floating-circle {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            animation: float-animation 10s infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes float-animation {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg);
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateY(-50px) rotate(360deg);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .error-number {
                font-size: 120px;
            }
            .error-message {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            .error-content {
                padding: 20px;
                margin: 0 20px;
            }
        }
        img{
            width: 300px;

        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    
           
    <div class="error-container">
        
        <div class="floating-elements">
           
            <div class="floating-circle" style="width: 200px; height: 200px; top: 10%; left: 10%; animation-delay: -2s;"></div>
            <div class="floating-circle" style="width: 300px; height: 300px; bottom: 20%; right: 15%; animation-delay: -5s;"></div>
            <div class="floating-circle" style="width: 150px; height: 150px; top: 70%; right: 5%; animation-delay: -7s;"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="error-content">
            <img id="logo" src="/img/footer-logo.png" alt="Logo">
            <div class="error-number">404</div>
            <h1 class="error-message">Rất tiếc! Không tìm thấy trang</h1>
            <p class="error-description">
                Xin lỗi, trang bạn đang tìm kiếm không tồn tại hoặc đã được di chuyển.
                Vui lòng kiểm tra URL hoặc quay lại trang chủ.
            </p>
            <a href="/" class="home-button">Quay lại Trang chủ</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
